HEADWORD: Improbity
<hw>Im*prob"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>improbitas</ets>; pref. <ets>im-</ets> not + <ets>probitas</ets>
probity: cf. F. <ets>improbit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety> <def>Lack of
